snippet.title: Cubiti Dash 'n' Dodge Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Here at Cube Headquarters, we are seriously crazy about cubes. We know that every single thing in the universe is better if it’s a cuboid.  Watermelons, flowers, humans, wheels; everything! 

Collect coins, dodge bombs and use epic powerups in Cubiti Dash 'n' Dodge for iOS and Android!
